✅ Day 77 – Problem: Convert a Number to Hexadecimal
Problem

Convert an integer into its hexadecimal representation without using built-in conversion methods.

Approach

Use bitwise AND (& 15) to extract hex digits

Map values 0–15 to corresponding hex characters

Use unsigned right shift to handle negative numbers

Reverse the final string for correct order

Complexity
Aspect	Value
Time	O(1)
Space	O(1)
Language	Java ☕
